{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927200/extras/Fail_01_crop.gif?t=1726303609\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EMBRACE THE FAILURE AND BECOME STRONGER FOR IT</h2>Drive to survive on ever-changing (procedural generation + handcrafting) tracks where everything is trying to stop you. Unlock permanent upgrades and get random temporary upgrades that change how you play each run. Every time you fail you move closer to your goals.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927200/extras/World_Balance_Showcase_600px_crop.gif?t=1726303609\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WORLD BALANCE MECHANIC</h2>The way you play the game, shapes the world around you. The game is build around two different playstyles - exposure vs. avoidance. Each approach has its own pros and cons and changes tracks, environments and access to upgrades, thus creating different experience.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927200/extras/Ability_Clean_crop.gif?t=1726303609\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FACE YOUR FEARS (OR DON'T)</h2>Use special powers to overcome ever-present danger. Will you CLEAR your mind of corruption or try to AVOID any threat?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>unique combination of racing genre and roguelite gameplay loop<br></li><li>gameplay mechanics that reflect real-world techniques of dealing with fear (exposure vs. avoidance)<br></li><li>unique \u201eWorld Balance\u201c mechanic that changes tracks, environments and access to upgrades<br></li><li>surreal setting with dreamy landscapes and nightmarish depictions<br></li><li>driving on the edge where every input matters</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726303609","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto